    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ufo 是一款简短的意识流视觉小说</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/c292463f448a3f5c94a26c075a6efc02.poster.avif?t=1761319405\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/c292463f448a3f5c94a26c075a6efc02.webm?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/c292463f448a3f5c94a26c075a6efc02.mp4?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UFO</strong>是少年在夏日的一场梦，他是一次碎片的，简短的，超现实主义的视觉体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/833014e367521c27b98dfe460e51500e.poster.avif?t=1761319405\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/833014e367521c27b98dfe460e51500e.webm?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/833014e367521c27b98dfe460e51500e.mp4?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>少年普兰（plan），处于中学时代，对一切的未知充满迷惑，和所有这一时期的孩子，对世界对人类充满未知的新奇，同时抱有恐惧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/dd17a4026d0c04e5bb9fac2158c6371e.poster.avif?t=1761319405\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/dd17a4026d0c04e5bb9fac2158c6371e.webm?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/dd17a4026d0c04e5bb9fac2158c6371e.mp4?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>他在梦里遇到，她，他们，它们。玩家扮演普兰，一起经历这场夏日的梦境。",
